### Variables
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7200
@token = 

### ============================================
### AUTHENTICATION
### ============================================

### Login to get JWT token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "123"
}

### ============================================
### ITEMS API (Requires Authentication)
### ============================================

### Get all items
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/items
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get item by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/items/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a new item
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/items
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Item",
  "description": "This is a test item description"
}

###

### Update item by ID
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/items/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Item Name",
  "description": "Updated description"
}

###

### Delete item by ID
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/items/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Test Error endpoint (No Auth Required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/items/TestError
Accept: application/json

###

### ============================================
### PRODUCTS API
### ============================================

### Get all products
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/product
Accept: application/json

###

### Get product by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/product/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a new product
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/product
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "id": 0,
  "name": "Sample Product",
  "price": 99.99,
  "category": "Electronics"
}

###

### Update product by ID
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/product/1
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "Updated Product Name",
  "price": 149.99,
  "category": "Electronics"
}

###

### Delete product by ID
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/product/1
Accept: application/json

